WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.929
Why did you save me?

2
00:00:04.929 --> 00:00:07.469
Take a guess.

3
00:00:07.469 --> 00:00:18.859
You see, it's far more entertaining to keep someone alive in pain.

4
00:00:18.859 --> 00:00:25.579
I plan to enjoy watching you suffer every single day.

5
00:00:25.579 --> 00:00:38.030
Maybe.

6
00:00:38.030 --> 00:00:39.350
Who knows?

7
00:00:39.350 --> 00:00:44.299
That should help a little.

8
00:00:44.299 --> 00:00:45.299
Someone told me that once.

9
00:00:45.299 --> 00:01:33.049
You're one already.

10
00:01:33.049 --> 00:01:36.840
Faster than I expected.

11
00:01:36.840 --> 00:01:50.650
Why can't you just admit that you're enjoying it?

12
00:01:50.650 --> 00:01:52.650
Don't understand what you're talking about.

13
00:01:52.650 --> 00:02:05.659
It's ill-allying to me.

14
00:02:05.659 --> 00:02:06.689
Okay.

15
00:02:06.689 --> 00:02:07.689
Never mind.

16
00:02:07.689 --> 00:02:12.400
Good night.

17
00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:30.520
I hope it affects you.

